creator: Abuzz
descriptionHtml:
An amazing combination of eggs, surprises, toys and animations is a guaranteed yummy recipe that will make your child happy. Your children will be thrilled while opening the cute chocolate eggs and collecting their favorite toys. The game is simple and easy to use even for the babies, - wait for the egg and then tap it with those little fingers to un-wrap the wrapper, now break the egg and open the plastic container to see the toy that you get to keep in your collection.

Great animations to entertain toddlers:
A game full of surprise, the egg comes in different creative ways that will make your kids love the app even more.

Choo–choo train – what is that sound; oh it’s a train wagon with an egg.
Hot air balloon – look up in the sky, do you see the egg in the basket, it’s coming down really fast.
Chicken lays an egg – our hen lays some funny looking eggs and you will love them.
Egg Balloon – did you know that you can blow air into the egg and make it bigger; we have the right tools, check it out.
Easter Rabbit – here comes the funny rabbit to bring us another chocolate egg.
Treasure box – you have three wooden boxes to open and find the hidden chocolate egg. Good luck!
“The Warp Pipe” – uh-oh some noises are coming out of that pipe, what can it be? Don’t worry, it’s a special egg with a new toy.
Lucky Spin wheel – spin the wheel and collect your surprise prize from our little carnival game.

If you have any feedback and suggestions on how we could further improve the design and interaction of our Kids apps and games, please visit our website www.iabuzz.com or leave us a message at kids@iabuzz.com
